Properties.RecordSource: Select String$(TaK3.Level*4," ") & IIf(Flag,IIf(TaK3.Open,Chr(150) & "  ","+  "),"    ") & Trim(TaK3.Name) As NameKO, Exists (Select * From TaK3 As Q Where (Q.Year=2001) And (Q.Курс=1) And (Q.Month=1) And (Q.Parent=TaK3.PKey)) As Flag, TaK3.* From TaK3 As TaK3_1 Right Join TaK3 On ((TaK3_1.P_R_D = TaK3.P_R_D) And (TaK3_1.PKey = TaK3.Parent) And (TaK3.Year = TaK3_1.Year) And (TaK3.Month = TaK3_1.Month)) Where ((TaK3.Parent Is Null) Or (TaK3_1.Open = True)) And (TaK3.P_R_D=1) And (TaK3.Year=2001) And (TaK3.Month=1) And (TaK3.Курс=1) Order By TaK3.PKey
